## Expected Results

By the end of this lab:

- Snake moves smoothly with joystick control
- All shared game state is mutex-protected (no visual corruption)
- Rendering only happens when the game state changes
- Fruit spawns randomly and never on the snake body
- Score increases when eating fruit; snake grows; speed increases
- Events (eating, game over) trigger distinct buzzer tones via an event group
- Cannot reverse direction instantly; self-collision ends the game
- Code is modular with separate files for each subsystem

