## Final Testing Checklist

Before demonstrating to a TA:

- [ ] Step 1: Starter runs; race conditions documented in report
- [ ] Step 2: No display corruption under rapid input; mutex hold time is minimal
- [ ] Step 3: Rendering only updates when the game state changes; render rate follows game speed
- [ ] Step 4: Red fruit appears at startup; never spawns on the snake; disappears when eaten
- [ ] Step 5: Score increments on eat; snake grows; game speeds up with score
- [ ] Step 6: High tone plays when eating; low tone plays on game over; tones do not block game tasks
- [ ] Step 7: Reverse direction ignored; self-collision stops game; S2 restarts cleanly

